{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778975504461,"sessionID":"ses_1cccfbadaffe3RHZq2a6RFT27P","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"apply_patch","callID":"call_qQPR18NYg2Kx3oMcGPuR6whj","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"patchText":"*** Begin Patch\n*** Add File: /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n+Addressed in PR #<NN>.\n+\n+Updated `dorsolateral prefrontal cortex` (`UBERON:0009834`) so its asserted `part_of` relationship now points to `prefrontal cortex` (`UBERON:0000451`) instead of directly to `cerebral cortex`.\n*** Add File: /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md\n+## Summary\n+\n+This change addresses issue #3447 by updating the asserted parentage of `dorsolateral prefrontal cortex` (`UBERON:0009834`).\n+\n+## Changes Made\n+\n+- Changed `UBERON:0009834` from `relationship: part_of UBERON:0000956 ! cerebral cortex` to `relationship: part_of UBERON:0000451 ! prefrontal cortex`.\n+- Preserved all other term metadata, xrefs, definition, and existing relationships.\n+\n+## Rationale\n+\n+The issue discussion notes that the Allen Brain Atlas hierarchy treats dorsolateral prefrontal cortex as part of prefrontal cortex. Since `prefrontal cortex` is already asserted as part of `cerebral cortex` in UBERON, this more specific `part_of` relationship retains the broader cerebral cortex placement through transitivity while correcting the directly asserted parent.\n+\n+## Checklist\n+\n+- Read imported issue context from `__issue_context__.json`.\n+- Inspected `UBERON:0009834`, `UBERON:0000451`, and `UBERON:0000956` using `obo-grep.pl`.\n+- Edited the term via `obo-checkout.pl` and `obo-checkin.pl` workflow.\n+- Reserialized `src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo` with `robot convert`.\n+- Narrowed the final diff to only the requested relationship change.\n+- Validated final OBO syntax with `robot convert`.\n+- Verified the updated target stanza with `obo-grep.pl`.\n+\n+## Validation\n+\n+- `robot convert -i src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo -f obo -o /tmp/opencode/uberon-edit-validation.obo` completed successfully.\n+- Final diff contains only the `part_of` target change for `UBERON:0009834`.\n+\n+@dragon-ai-agent\n*** End Patch"},"output":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\nA PR_COMMENTS.md","metadata":{"diff":"Index: /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,3 @@\n+Addressed in PR #<NN>.\n+\n+Updated `dorsolateral prefrontal cortex` (`UBERON:0009834`) so its asserted `part_of` relationship now points to `prefrontal cortex` (`UBERON:0000451`) instead of directly to `cerebral cortex`.\n\nIndex: /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,29 @@\n+## Summary\n+\n+This change addresses issue #3447 by updating the asserted parentage of `dorsolateral prefrontal cortex` (`UBERON:0009834`).\n+\n+## Changes Made\n+\n+- Changed `UBERON:0009834` from `relationship: part_of UBERON:0000956 ! cerebral cortex` to `relationship: part_of UBERON:0000451 ! prefrontal cortex`.\n+- Preserved all other term metadata, xrefs, definition, and existing relationships.\n+\n+## Rationale\n+\n+The issue discussion notes that the Allen Brain Atlas hierarchy treats dorsolateral prefrontal cortex as part of prefrontal cortex. Since `prefrontal cortex` is already asserted as part of `cerebral cortex` in UBERON, this more specific `part_of` relationship retains the broader cerebral cortex placement through transitivity while correcting the directly asserted parent.\n+\n+## Checklist\n+\n+- Read imported issue context from `__